text: Ikhtisad () is a rural locality (a village) in Meneuztamaksky Selsoviet, Miyakinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 102 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 33 km from Kirgiz-Miyaki, 5 km from Meneuztamak. == References == Category:Rural localities in Miyakinsky District
title: Ikhtisad
